Enterprise Sales Manager
Wavecrest Payment Technology Pvt Ltd
Location:
Hyderabad
Job Details
Industry
Information Technology (IT) / eCommerce/ CRM
Functional Area
Service Sales
Desired Candidate Profile
8-10 years of significant experience in successful enterprise software sales experience in India, Middle East and Africa.
Preferable Industry knowledge and experience required in Insurance/Financial Services / Enterprise Banking.
Proven track record of driving and closing multimillion dollar enterprise deals.
An understanding of and proficiency with demonstrating software solutions.
Proficiency in the sales processes and account/territory planning.
Proficiency in solution selling in complex sales cycles with C-Level interaction and strong closing skills.
Capable of driving sales process, proposal writing and contract negotiation.
Connect and Actively engage with key influencers and decision makers inside an organization.
Superior oral and written communication and presentation skills.
Outstanding Customer focused account management skills.
Ability to travel is a must.
Qualification
Any Graduate
OR
Any Postgraduate
Experience
8
to
10
Years
Job Description
Identify and own new client contact, acquisition, growth & retention of predefined priority target customers.
Identify and build strategy to capitalize on all major contacts at Executive, Departmental level within company.
Identify key business drivers, pre-existing vendor relationship, agencies involved, third party systems & more.
Handle priority client management, optimization, and relationship development.
Provide accurate forecasting on status of business plan, achievements completed, challenges encountered, and plan for moving forward on predefined priority accounts.
